      "label": "rule_extractor",
      "instructions": "Analyze the provided 45 rules of the board game. Identify all rules that mention the butterfly, the fish, or any intermediate entities that could link them. Create a directed mapping of cause-and-effect relationships or conditional triggers involving these specific entities."
    },
