      "label": "logic_verifier",
      "instructions": "Using the mapping of rules provided, attempt to construct a logical chain of events that starts with the butterfly and ends with the fish revealing a secret. Determine if the rules provide enough information to confirm this happens, confirm it cannot happen, or if the information is insufficient to reach a conclusion."
    }
